      give the user the option to go to different music apps that allow a person to listen to music. 
      </p>
      <p class= "hey"> In the Home page, there is a search bar where the user types in a key word related to what they want to look up.
      At the bottom of the search bar, the user has the option of choosing the artist, album, playlist, and track. The user
      clicks the submit button and they are taken to a page that contains the information they searched for. Depending on the 
      option that user chose, they will either be taken to the Artist page, Album page, Playlist page, or the Track page.
      </p>
      <p> This app was created to make a user's life easier when searching for information about their favorite artists,
